            <lg xml:id="TK537">
<l>ariyaveṉ ṟākāta villaipoc cāvāk </l>
<l>karuviyāṟ pōṟṟic ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is nothing too difficult to be accomplished, if a man set about it carefully, with unflinching endeavour.</l>
